```toml
# === RAG ===
fastembed = "5"
hnsw_rs = "0.3"
anndists = "0.1"

# Document parsing
pdf-extract = "0.7"
scraper = "0.20"
csv = "1"
encoding_rs = "0.8"

# Storage & serialization
rusqlite = { version = "0.32", features = ["bundled"] }  # if not already present
bincode = "1.3"

# Utilities
uuid = { version = "1", features = ["v4"] }
sha2 = "0.10"
```

**Do NOT add:** `tiktoken-rs` (too heavy), `docx-rs` (limited value, add later), `memmap2` (premature optimization). Keep the dependency surface small.

