## Implementation Order (4 phases)

### Phase 1 — Data Foundation
1. `src-backend/src/db/rag.rs` — SQLite schema + CRUD functions
2. `src-backend/src/rag/config.rs` — Config struct + load/save
3. `src-backend/src/rag/ingestion.rs` — File parsers + chunking (txt, md, pdf only to start)
4. `src-backend/src/rag/mod.rs` — Wire up module

### Phase 2 — Embedding + Vector Store
5. `src-backend/src/rag/embedding.rs` — FastembedEmbedder (primary) + LlamaCppEmbedder
6. `src-backend/src/rag/vectorstore.rs` — HNSW wrapper with persist/load
7. `src-backend/src/state.rs` — Add RAG fields to AppState
8. `src-backend/src/main.rs` — Initialize RAG state at startup

### Phase 3 — Pipeline + API
9. `src-backend/src/rag/retrieval.rs` — Full retrieval pipeline
10. `src-backend/src/rag/augmentation.rs` — Prompt builder
11. `src-backend/src/services/rag.rs` — Ingestion orchestrator (parse → chunk → embed → store)
12. `src-backend/src/routes/rag.rs` — All REST endpoints
13. Modify existing chat route to support `collection_id`

### Phase 4 — Frontend
14. `src-frontend/src/lib/ragApi.ts`
15. `src-frontend/src/stores/ragStore.ts`
16. `src-frontend/src/pages/KnowledgeBase.tsx`
17. `src-frontend/src/components/rag/*` — all 6 components
18. Wire into App.tsx routing + existing chat components

